                <p class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-picton-blue-500 uppercase"> More Than Just A Career </p> 
                <h1 class="mt-0 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-muted-700 dark:text-white  sm:text-4xl"> Should You Become A Pilot? </h1> 
                <p class="mt-6 text-xl leading-8 text-muted-700 dark:text-white ">At <strong>Blue Skies Above</strong>, we understand that the call to fly is more than just a hobby—it's a calling. Our expert instructors are dedicated to sharing their passion, providing the skills and knowledge you need to command the skies with confidence. From the unmatched thrill of your first solo to launching a professional career, our flight school is your launchpad to a rewarding life in aviation.</p> 
